<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>사케나 야코비</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/sakena_yacoobi_how_i_stopped_the_taliban_from_shutting_down_my_school?language=ko' lang='ko'>
나는 어떻게 학교를 폐쇄하려는 탈레반을 막았는가
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Sep 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Courageous
